description:
The legendary lost third PAVLOV`S DOG album

Recorded 1977 and originally titeled "HAS ANYONE HERE SEEN SIGFRIED". For the first time ever regulary released 2007 by Rockville plus 10 bonustracks containing a compilation of rare and unreleased live and studio recordings 1974-77.

- 10 original tracks, recorded 1977

- plus 10 bonustracks

- total time 79:53 minutes

- digitally remastered
